Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双  双  双钻头…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:40.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双  双  双钻头…
